&lt;p&gt;As the &lt;strong&gt;Demand Generation Manager,&lt;/strong&gt; you are responsible for planning, executing, and optimizing integrated demand generation programs that drive awareness, engagement, pipeline creation, and revenue growth. Working closely with Product Marketing, Growth Marketing, Sales, Revenue Operations, and regional marketing teams, you translate strategic priorities into scalable campaigns and programs that engage target audiences throughout the buyer journey. Success in this role requires strong demand generation expertise, analytical rigor, cross-functional collaboration, and the ability to leverage AI-enabled insights and technologies to improve marketing performance and business outcomes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
