&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and execute integrated demand generation programs across digital, paid media, content, webinars, events, lifecycle marketing, and account-based marketing initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate business objectives, campaign priorities, and go-to-market strategies into measurable demand generation plans.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Product Marketing, Growth Marketing, and Sales teams to align campaign messaging, audience targeting, and program execution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support audience segmentation, account targeting, buying-group engagement, and campaign planning activities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage campaign timelines, deliverables, and stakeholder communications to ensure effective execution.&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
