&lt;li&gt;Analyze campaign data and performance trends to improve targeting, conversion rates, and marketing effectiveness.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Marketing Operations and Revenue Operations to support attribution, reporting, campaign measurement, and 6sense strategy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop performance reports, dashboards, and recommendations for marketing stakeholders and leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Apply testing methodologies and continuous optimization practices to improve program outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
