&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Overview &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As the &lt;strong&gt;Digital Marketing Operations Specialist,&lt;/strong&gt; you are responsible for supporting the day-to-day execution, publishing, maintenance, and optimization of Rithum&#39;s website and digital content ecosystem. Working closely with Marketing, Product Marketing, Creative, Legal, and external partners, you execute website updates, content publishing, SEO enhancements, quality assurance testing, and content governance activities that ensure a high-quality digital experience. Success in this role requires strong attention to detail, technical aptitude, organizational skills, and the ability to leverage digital tools, analytics, and AI-enabled technologies to improve website performance, operational efficiency, and content discoverability.&lt;/p&gt;
