&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain account-level scoring models combining firmographic, technographic, behavioural, and intent signals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Refresh ICP on a defined cadence as market dynamics, win/loss patterns, and product mix evolve&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Account &amp;amp; Contact Strategy
&lt;ul&gt;
